reviewText:
I have watched this 20 Times and shared it with a dozen people
It is a gem
You don't have to be Jewish to love it
I love this, helps to explore Jewish Identity, gives some history and does a lot to stimulate conversation with friends.
This is possibly the best documentary I've ever watched, and it's only 18 minutes long. Way to change the game!

This is a great video to watch whether you are a Barbie fan or not. It won the Sundance Film Festival award and it is a great video to have in your collection. It is not available for rental, netflix, hulu or torrent. Buy it and enjoy.

This 18-minute movie alternately had me laughing out loud and reeling internally from its sheer profundity.  Just about all you'll ever need to know about the Jewish people and Barbie.  But maybe I'm biased, because I'm MOT.
